<node>
    <interface name="org.gnome.Shell.Extensions.WindowsExt">
        <method name="List">
            <arg type="s" direction="out" name="win"/>
        </method>
        <method name="FocusTitle">
            <arg type="s" direction="out" />
        </method>
        <method name="FocusPID">
            <arg type="s" direction="out" />
        </method>
        <method name="FocusClass">
            <arg type="s" direction="out" />
        </method>
    </interface>
</node>
